

# Wesley Glass Screensaver

An elegant, audio-reactive fullscreen glass gradient screensaver designed for laptops and desktops.

## 🌟 Features

- 🎨 Amber + Midnight glowing gradient background
- 💡 Diagonal animation flow every 3s
- 🎙️ Audio-triggered pulse animation via microphone input
- 🖱️ Mouse ripple effect that follows your cursor
- 💎 Frosted glass nav bar with:
  - “Look @ God” in Allura cursive font
  - “Builder. Believer. Creative Mind.”

## 📂 File Structure

- `index.html` – Core HTML layout
- `style.css` – All animations, glass effects, and styling
- `script.js` – Microphone + audio detection logic + ripple effects

## 🔧 Setup

1. Clone or download the project
2. Open `index.html` in your browser
3. Allow microphone access when prompted
4. Enjoy the vibe ✨

## 🖥️ Use Case

Perfect for showcasing your style on idle screens — whether you're working in coffee shops, coding in public, or meeting with potential clients.

